**Issue :** 

When users share a specific job update or the homepage on social media, there is no dynamic OpenGraph preview. The project has an og-image.svg, but it is not dynamically populated with job data.
Improvement: Implement dynamic metadata in the Next.js layout.tsx or individual page components to improve social sharing visibility.

**File Path** :  `open-source-jobs/app/layout.tsx`

**Code logic :**

```
export const metadata = {
  title: 'Open Source Jobs',
  description: 'Find jobs at companies building open source software.',
  openGraph: {
    images: ['/og-image.svg'],
  },
};
```
